1
00:02:22,160 --> 00:02:27,320
- Martial God Asura S2 -

2
00:02:28,200 --> 00:02:32,880
Episode 9
[Battle at Sword God Valley]
FANSUB: H-DONGHUA™

3
00:02:34,000 --> 00:02:36,880
(Azure Dragon Sect.
Ancestral Tomb Mountain)

4
00:02:37,040 --> 00:02:38,160
(Ancestral Tomb Mountain)

5
00:02:47,740 --> 00:02:50,500
Today,
I'll destroy your ancestors' tombs

6
00:02:50,580 --> 00:02:53,220
to avenge my son's spirit!

7
00:03:36,560 --> 00:03:40,800
(Azure)

8
00:03:42,540 --> 00:03:44,220
An eye for an eye,

9
00:03:44,300 --> 00:03:45,900
a tooth for a tooth.

10
00:03:46,780 --> 00:03:49,860
I'll make Sword God Valley pay.

11
00:03:53,580 --> 00:03:54,740
I'll go with you.

12
00:03:56,900 --> 00:03:58,539
This journey is full of danger.

13
00:03:58,540 --> 00:03:59,980
I can't let you take the risk alone.

14
00:04:00,860 --> 00:04:02,059
An eye for an eye,

15
00:04:02,060 --> 00:04:03,340
a tooth for a tooth.

16
00:04:03,460 --> 00:04:04,940
You said that yourself.

17
00:04:06,180 --> 00:04:08,220
If you're willing
to risk your life for me,

18
00:04:08,660 --> 00:04:10,420
then so am I for you.

19
00:04:10,900 --> 00:04:11,860
Okay.

20
00:04:12,800 --> 00:04:16,360
(Azure)

21
00:04:16,440 --> 00:04:19,560
(Tea House)

22
00:04:24,780 --> 00:04:25,780
Shoo!

23
00:04:25,940 --> 00:04:27,820
Do you think this is a charity house?

24
00:04:33,220 --> 00:04:36,060
Boss, give me a pot of Immortal Brew

25
00:04:36,180 --> 00:04:39,540
and some peanuts for my boys.

26
00:04:48,600 --> 00:04:51,960
So, do you think the Azure Dragon Sect
will show up?

27
00:04:52,760 --> 00:04:54,000
Probably not.

28
00:04:54,280 --> 00:04:55,679
When our Valley Master
stormed their sect,

29
00:04:55,680 --> 00:04:57,040
not a single soul was there.

30
00:04:57,240 --> 00:04:58,640
They ran off clean.

31
00:04:59,240 --> 00:05:01,039
Zhang Tianyi killed the Young Master,

32
00:05:01,040 --> 00:05:02,239
took the Divine Wood Sword,

33
00:05:02,240 --> 00:05:04,960
and now he's hiding like a coward.

34
00:05:07,600 --> 00:05:08,719
Digging up their ancestors' graves,

35
00:05:08,720 --> 00:05:10,800
even roasting their bones
over the sword-forging pool?

36
00:05:11,040 --> 00:05:12,720
Our Valley Master is ruthless.

37
00:05:14,040 --> 00:05:15,419
Cross Sword God Valley,

38
00:05:15,420 --> 00:05:17,150
and that's your fate.

39
00:05:20,170 --> 00:05:23,080
Kid, how dare you splash wine
on my face?!

40
00:05:23,440 --> 00:05:26,400
It's wasted on scum like you anyway.

41
00:05:26,720 --> 00:05:28,840
What a waste of good wine.

42
00:05:29,240 --> 00:05:30,360
You!

43
00:05:32,360 --> 00:05:33,920
Why won't it come out?!

44
00:05:38,520 --> 00:05:39,400
It won't budge?

45
00:05:46,440 --> 00:05:50,120
You're Chu Feng of Azure Dragon Sect?

46
00:06:03,160 --> 00:06:04,280
What are you doing?

47
00:06:04,760 --> 00:06:06,200
What's the meaning of this?

48
00:06:07,440 --> 00:06:08,640
Take this!

49
00:06:10,280 --> 00:06:11,599
I've got no grudge against you.

50
00:06:11,600 --> 00:06:13,160
Why draw your blade on me?

51
00:06:31,560 --> 00:06:32,519
The Divine Wood Sword?

52
00:06:32,520 --> 00:06:33,960
Could it be...

53
00:06:41,280 --> 00:06:43,280
What a nice move
that Lightning Triple Strike is!

54
00:06:45,880 --> 00:06:47,400
It just so happens that I know it too.

55
00:06:52,880 --> 00:06:53,960
Hahaha!

56
00:06:54,440 --> 00:06:55,480
After all these years,

57
00:06:55,600 --> 00:06:56,879
I never thought that after me,

58
00:06:56,880 --> 00:06:58,639
Azure Dragon Sect
would finally produce another

59
00:06:58,640 --> 00:07:00,120
who mastered Lightning Triple Strike.

60
00:07:02,520 --> 00:07:05,200
Stop, Senior Tianyi.

61
00:07:16,040 --> 00:07:18,160
I didn't mean
to make things difficult just now.

62
00:07:18,640 --> 00:07:20,650
Sword God Valley is extremely dangerous,

63
00:07:21,400 --> 00:07:22,680
so I had to test you.

64
00:07:22,920 --> 00:07:24,480
That makes some sense

65
00:07:24,560 --> 00:07:25,960
but I'm still not pleased.

66
00:07:26,520 --> 00:07:27,439
Besides,

67
00:07:27,440 --> 00:07:29,239
I've heard this whole disaster
for Azure Dragon Sect

68
00:07:29,240 --> 00:07:31,360
started because of you.

69
00:07:33,000 --> 00:07:34,920
Did you really kill Murong Yu?

70
00:07:35,720 --> 00:07:37,439
We wagered the Divine Wood Sword

71
00:07:37,440 --> 00:07:39,000
and sparred,

72
00:07:39,120 --> 00:07:40,640
but I never harmed him.

73
00:07:40,960 --> 00:07:44,859
Yet rumors say
someone witnessed it firsthand.

74
00:07:44,860 --> 00:07:46,560
Something's not right.

75
00:07:57,320 --> 00:07:58,680
What they saw...

76
00:08:02,060 --> 00:08:03,350
was indeed you.

77
00:08:04,240 --> 00:08:05,479
Murong Yu's death

78
00:08:05,480 --> 00:08:06,199
was Yan Yangtian's doing.

79
00:08:06,200 --> 00:08:07,679
He used this strange artifact
to disguise himself

80
00:08:07,680 --> 00:08:08,920
and pin the blame on you.

81
00:08:09,080 --> 00:08:10,999
He deliberately stirred conflict
between the sects,

82
00:08:11,000 --> 00:08:12,679
so those behind him

83
00:08:12,680 --> 00:08:14,080
could control all of the Nine Provinces.

84
00:08:16,000 --> 00:08:20,080
Both Azure Dragon Sect
and Sword God Valley were just pawns?

85
00:08:20,600 --> 00:08:22,919
But Sword God Valley struck first,
without regard for right or wrong,

86
00:08:22,920 --> 00:08:24,680
and then desecrated our ancestral tombs.

87
00:08:25,320 --> 00:08:27,600
This injustice must be repaid.

88
00:08:28,880 --> 00:08:32,440
Then we'll wipe them out
to the last man.

89
00:08:35,800 --> 00:08:38,600
(Sword God Valley.
Underground Stone Hall)

90
00:08:52,560 --> 00:08:53,480
Ancestor,

91
00:08:54,280 --> 00:08:57,119
all external disciples
have been recalled.

92
00:08:57,120 --> 00:08:58,599
Everything is in place.

93
00:08:58,600 --> 00:09:00,960
We're just waiting for Zhang Tianyi
to walk into our trap.

94
00:09:01,480 --> 00:09:04,999
But he has always kept a low profile,

95
00:09:05,000 --> 00:09:07,920
and now Azure Dragon Sect
has been pushed to this point.

96
00:09:08,030 --> 00:09:11,630
Murong Yu's death seems suspicious.

97
00:09:25,760 --> 00:09:29,560
Yu was Sword God Valley's only future.

98
00:09:29,880 --> 00:09:31,559
(Murong Heng,
Ancestor of Sword God Valley)

99
00:09:31,560 --> 00:09:33,640
(Heaven Martial Fourth Level)

100
00:09:33,920 --> 00:09:36,639
Now he's been killed,

101
00:09:36,640 --> 00:09:38,719
and you're cowering in fear.

102
00:09:38,720 --> 00:09:41,080
Jow will you answer to our ancestors?

103
00:09:41,240 --> 00:09:42,879
But Azure Dragon Sect

104
00:09:42,880 --> 00:09:44,760
has the Jiang Dynasty backing them.

105
00:09:45,100 --> 00:09:47,639
It's just a hollow dynasty,
all show and no substance.

106
00:09:47,640 --> 00:09:49,120
What is there to fear?

107
00:09:49,400 --> 00:09:51,520
Whoever Sword God Valley wants dead,

108
00:09:51,920 --> 00:09:54,050
dies.

109
00:09:56,920 --> 00:09:57,760
Yes, sir.

110
00:09:59,840 --> 00:10:03,440
(Sword God Valley.
Valley Entrance Square)

111
00:10:06,520 --> 00:10:07,599
Their ancestral graves were dug up,

112
00:10:07,600 --> 00:10:08,479
their remains stolen.

113
00:10:08,480 --> 00:10:11,080
Those Azure Dragon Sect cowards
are too scared to even show up.

114
00:10:11,120 --> 00:10:12,399
With the Sword God Formation

115
00:10:12,400 --> 00:10:13,999
left by our founding ancestor
protecting the valley,

116
00:10:14,000 --> 00:10:15,399
no matter how many come,

117
00:10:15,400 --> 00:10:16,760
they'll all die.

118
00:10:24,960 --> 00:10:26,160
Sword God Valley,

119
00:10:27,280 --> 00:10:29,040
your end is here!

120
00:10:29,064 --> 00:11:03,864
(Watch the Latest Donghua Episodes: www.h-donghua.xyz)

121
00:11:04,480 --> 00:11:06,480
Murong Yi, get out here!

122
00:11:08,760 --> 00:11:10,400
You've got some nerve showing up here.

123
00:11:12,240 --> 00:11:15,280
Insolent brat, you have a death wish!

124
00:11:36,360 --> 00:11:37,760
Kill them!

125
00:11:37,880 --> 00:11:39,879
- Kill them!
- Kill!

126
00:11:39,880 --> 00:11:41,440
Avenge the Young Master!

127
00:11:57,040 --> 00:11:58,939
I'll go teach
that blind old fool a lesson

128
00:11:58,940 --> 00:12:00,790
for not knowing right from wrong.

129
00:12:03,480 --> 00:12:06,679
Zhang Tianyi,
I'll rip out your heart today

130
00:12:06,680 --> 00:12:09,080
to honor my son!

131
00:12:09,400 --> 00:12:11,199
You can't even tell right from wrong,

132
00:12:11,200 --> 00:12:13,240
and you dare call yourself
a Valley Master?

133
00:12:29,800 --> 00:12:31,200
I'll deal with the small fry.

134
00:12:36,840 --> 00:12:38,000
(Found it.)

135
00:12:38,280 --> 00:12:39,400
(It's underground.)

136
00:12:39,760 --> 00:12:41,600
(There's a powerful surge
of mystic power.)

137
00:12:41,760 --> 00:12:44,320
It's released by someone at least
at the Heaven Martial Fourth Level.

138
00:12:44,440 --> 00:12:46,280
(Let's split the ground open first.)

139
00:13:02,160 --> 00:13:03,919
Run!

140
00:13:03,920 --> 00:13:05,760
Ancestor, they're here!

141
00:13:18,280 --> 00:13:20,000
Perfect timing.

142
00:13:21,160 --> 00:13:22,919
Today,
I'll use these Azure Dragon Sect scum

143
00:13:22,920 --> 00:13:24,120
as living sacrifices

144
00:13:24,160 --> 00:13:26,440
to activate the Sword God Formation

145
00:13:26,600 --> 00:13:28,800
and avenge my grandson!

146
00:13:53,000 --> 00:13:54,999
Chu Feng, they're being controlled
by the formation

147
00:13:55,000 --> 00:13:56,369
like walking dead.

148
00:13:56,370 --> 00:13:57,660
I'm not afraid of the living.

149
00:13:58,430 --> 00:14:00,640
You think I'll fear the dead?

150
00:14:28,160 --> 00:14:29,120
The remains.

151
00:14:30,920 --> 00:14:32,389
Trying to take them?

152
00:14:32,390 --> 00:14:33,400
Dream on!

153
00:15:04,890 --> 00:15:06,159
You're courting death!

154
00:15:06,160 --> 00:15:08,080
Hahaha.

155
00:15:08,780 --> 00:15:10,949
And you call yourself a Sword Saint?

156
00:15:10,950 --> 00:15:14,039
Why not hand that title
over to me instead?

157
00:15:14,040 --> 00:15:15,679
Zhang Tianyi,

158
00:15:15,680 --> 00:15:17,600
your life ends here!

159
00:15:39,520 --> 00:15:41,320
I'll kill you!

160
00:15:48,600 --> 00:15:50,720
Then try it.

161
00:16:22,040 --> 00:16:23,199
Yi!

162
00:16:23,200 --> 00:16:25,280
You brought this on yourself.

163
00:16:26,560 --> 00:16:28,280
Zhang Tianyi!

164
00:16:28,500 --> 00:16:29,789
First you killed my grandson,

165
00:16:29,790 --> 00:16:31,160
then my son!

166
00:16:31,360 --> 00:16:34,119
Today, I'll carve you to pieces

167
00:16:34,120 --> 00:16:36,920
and grind your bones to ash!

168
00:16:36,944 --> 00:17:07,244
FANSUB: H-DONGHUA™

